    {
      "kind": "parameters",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The hint to display.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "hint"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This text will appear next to the Action Button to describe what your",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "control will do when activated. By default, a control’s action hint is",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "derived from its display name, the type of control, and value text, if",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "any:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "// Action Hint: “Hold for ‘Ping My Watch’”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "struct PingMyWatchButton: Control {",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "static let displayName: LocalizedStringResource = “Ping My Watch”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "…",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "// When this button’s action conforms to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "OpenIntent",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ":",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "// Action Hint: “Hold to Open Notes”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "struct NotesLauncher: Control {",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "static let displayName: LocalizedStringResource = “Notes”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "…",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "// Action Hint: “Hold to Turn On ‘Silent Mode’” / “Hold to Turn Off ‘Silent Mode’”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "struct SilentModeToggle: Control {",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "static let displayName: LocalizedStringResource = “Silent Mode”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "…",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "// Action Hint: “Hold for Silent” / “Hold for Ring”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "ControlWidgetToggle(…) { isOn in",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Label(",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "isOn ? “Silent” : “Ring”,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "systemImage: isOn ? “bell.slash” : “bell”",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": ")",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the default action hint is insufficiently descriptive, you can",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "customize the hint by applying this modifier to the control’s label.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For instance, we can describe what the user will use our",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "NotesLauncher",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " control to do, “Compose a Note”, instead of the default",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "“Hold to Open Notes” hint, like this:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "ControlWidgetButton(…) {",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Image(systemName: “note.text”)",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": ".controlWidgetActionHint(“Compose a Note”)",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "}",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
